Interface SwipeDismissListViewTouchListener.DismissCallbacks

  • Enclosing class:
    SwipeDismissListViewTouchListener

    public static interface SwipeDismissListViewTouchListener.DismissCallbacks
    The callback interface used by SwipeDismissListViewTouchListener to inform its client about a successful dismissal of one or more list item positions.
